WEBVTT

08:31.550 --> 08:33.030
Just come in and sit.

08:33.230 --> 08:34.870
I do not want
to come in and sit.

08:35.070 --> 08:36.790
This will just take a minute.

08:36.990 --> 08:39.350
You say that and then we spend
the whole day here.

08:44.980 --> 08:46.630
She might blow
the entire building up.

08:46.830 --> 08:47.940
Then let her.

09:03.250 --> 09:05.730
You have to stop helping
these people!

09:05.930 --> 09:08.460
You don't work here anymore.

09:09.880 --> 09:11.110
They didn't know there was
a higher shelf

09:11.310 --> 09:12.870
in the linen closet.

09:13.060 --> 09:16.160
They forgot how to stack wood
in a fireplace.

09:16.360 --> 09:19.160
A bird flew in
and they could not think...

09:19.360 --> 09:22.330
...to just open a window
to let it out.

09:22.530 --> 09:24.340
They are grown people.

09:24.530 --> 09:25.670
They have to learn
to take care of themselves.

09:25.870 --> 09:26.810
They can't!

09:28.480 --> 09:31.130
Back in the old country...

09:31.330 --> 09:36.430
...when a horse is lame,
it is useless, so you shoot it.

09:36.630 --> 09:40.660
This is an entire house full of
extremely lame horses!

09:43.870 --> 09:46.250
Do not answer the phone!

36:53.460 --> 36:56.030
They call and you come running.

36:56.230 --> 36:57.610
Like a well-trained Spaniel.

36:57.810 --> 36:58.740
Stop it, Janusz.

36:58.940 --> 37:00.950
We should get you a leash
and a chew toy.

37:01.150 --> 37:02.090
Shut it!

37:29.030 --> 37:32.410
This is why they always want
to kill the fancy folks.
